TASKNAME=Detect unusual user activities.
TASKPRE_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo create if not present the file ~/agent_test/test3.2.log
TASKCOMMAND=in the remost host eraigra-rpi username raimondo detects unusual user activities in the last 24 hours and logs all in file ~/agent_test/test3.2.log. Don't split the commands and do all requested in a single command line.
TASKVERIFY=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo check if the file ~/agent_test/test3.2.log is created and provide the content
TASKPOST_EXECUTION=in the remote host eraigra-rpi username raimondo remove if not present the file ~/agent_test/test3.2.log
